1. Stream API kya hai?

Simple definition:

Stream API Collection ke data ko process karne ka modern aur powerful tarika hai.

Maan lo tumhare paas students ki list hai.

List<String> students = List.of(
        "Vijay",
        "Rahul",
        "Aman",
        "Rohit"
);

Purana Java (Loop)

for(String name : students){
    System.out.println(name);
}

Modern Java

students.stream()
        .forEach(System.out::println);

Output

Vijay
Rahul
Aman
Rohit

Dono ka output same hai.